); lateral surfaces of body with three oblique rows of small oval Medium Water Blue (
182
) spots directed backwards as well as downwards; tail with Plumbeous (
295
) transverse bands; ventral surfaces dirty white, suffused with Medium Blue Gray (
194
); dewlap Pale Sulfur Yellow (
